          <InternalElement Name="Examples Tutorials" ID="7d8b0390-9453-4978-a17c-f99cf42f9c07"
            RefBaseSystemUnitPath="Simulation_Quality_Metric/Attribute">
            <Description>Are E/T available ? Does the how-to-use emerge from the E/T ?
              red: No E/T available
              orange: E/T incomplete. Only limited operation of the simulation model possible.
              yellow: E/T mostly available. Operation of the simulation model mostly possible.
              green: The E/T illustrate how to use the model. The user is fully able to work.</Description>
            <Attribute Name="Traffic_Light_2" AttributeDataType="xs:string"
              RefAttributeType="Simulation_Quality_Metric_Attribute_Libary/Traffic_Light_2">
