            RefBaseSystemUnitPath="Simulation_Quality_Metric/Attribute">
            <Description>This is a tool-dependet criterion and a purely distinguishing feater.
              Therefore it has no effect on the result of the quality metric.

              Is the model know-how protected, e.g. a compiled model
              (binary FMU, black-box, …)</Description>
            <Attribute Name="Closed_Question" AttributeDataType="xs:string"
              RefAttributeType="Simulation_Quality_Metric_Attribute_Libary/Closed_Question">
